" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Starting Zone:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Qeynos, South&Comment=1">Qeynos, South</a></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Secondary Zones:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=&Comment=1"></a></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Items Needed:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Bandit Sash</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Description:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>1.</b> This quest begins in South Qeynos.  Head to the House of Thunder and look for <b>Chesgard Sydwen</b> at loc -280 -500.  He explains that he will give you a random item and some gold if you bring him a Bandit Sash.
<br><br>
<b>2.</b> <b>Bandit Sashes</b>, as you might imagine, are dropped by <b>Bandits</b>.  They can be found in several zones throughout Norrath.  Some include East Karana (loc +1500 -650), West Karana (loc +50 -7880), and Rathe Mountains (+3000 +1300).  Simply choose a zone and kill the bandits until you obtain a Bandit Sash.  Bandits range from level 9 to 12.
<br><br>
<b>3.</b> To make your trip more worthwhile, bring as many Bandit Sashes as you can carry to complete the quest over and over again.
<br><br>
<b>4.</b> Now return to South Qeynos and give your Bandit Sashes to <b>Chesgard</b>.  He will then give you some gold, a bronze weapon or a shield, and the following faction adjustments:
<br><br>
+ Guards of Qeynos<br>
+ Knights of Thunder<br>
+ Priests of Life<br>
- Blood Sabres</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Author:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Wraith (Bristlebane)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Quest Reward:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>Random Bronze Weapon or Shield</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma"></font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>Random</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rating:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>6.5</b> (average of <b>25</b> votes)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rate this quest:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><FORM ACTION = "ratequest.asp" METHOD = post><SELECT NAME="Voting"><OPTION VALUE="0">Rate this Quest</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="1">1 - Don't waste your time</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="2">2</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="3">3</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="4">4</OPTION><OPTION VALUE="5">5 - It is ok</OPTION>